{% extends "::base.html.twig" %}

{% block title %}Blog Archive{% endblock %}

{% block body %}
<h1>Blog Archive</h1>
{% for post in posts %}

  <div class="media">
    <div class="media-left">
      <a href="#">
        <img alt="64x64" class="media-object" data-src="holder.js/64x64" style="width: 64px; height: 64px;" src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," data-holder-rendered="true">
      </a>
    </div>
    <div class="media-body">
      <h4 class="media-heading"><a href="{{ path('post_show', {'slug': post.slug}) }}">{{ post.title }}</a></h4>
      {{ post.publishDate|date("Y-m-d") }} - Pellentesque malesuada augue libero, quis eleifend nisl posuere nec. Nulla eu vehicula urna, sit amet scelerisque mi. Nullam porta ipsum diam, quis commodo ex semper vitae. Aenean vel erat lobortis, fermentum metus vitae, dapibus dolor. Duis maximus sed mauris vitae consequat.
    </div>
  </div>

{% endfor %}

{% endblock %}
